om sidebar buttons\n\n6. **UI Improvements**\n   - Chatbox: 15sp text, 44dp buttons, tighter spacing (2-4dp)\n   - Better send icon (ic_send.xml)\n   - Attach image icon matches generate button color (@color/primary)\n   - Smaller conversation text (14sp), reduced padding (12dp)\n   - Bold text for current conversation in sidebar\n\n7. **Error Handling**\n   - Try-catch blocks everywhere\n   - Safe array access with getOrNull()\n   - Bounds checking before removing items\n   - Job cancellation on delete/clear/switch\n   - No crashes on theme change, conversation switch, or AI response\n\n8. **Image Generation**\n   - Uses direct pollinations.ai URL when no API key\n   - Format: `https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/{encoded_prompt}?width=1024&height=1024&model=flux&nologo=true`\n   - Works as first message in chat\n\n9. **State Persistence**\n   - onPause/onStop save chat history\n   - Theme changes save before switching\n   - Loading messages filtered out when saving\n   - Current conversation ID tracked\n\n10. **Toolbar Features**\n    - Dark mode toggle\n    - Model selection\n    - New chat button (only if current chat not empty)\n    - Clear chat\n    - Overflow menu: System Instructions, API Key Settings\n\n## TECHNICAL CONTEXT\n\n### Key Files\n- **MainActivity.kt** (850+ lines)\n  - `conversationManager: ConversationManager`\n  - `currentConversationId: String`\n  - `systemPrompt: String`\n  - `conversationAdapter: ConversationAdapter?`\n  - `chatJob: Job?`\n\n- **ConversationAdapter.kt**\n  - `isSelectionMode: Boolean`\n  - `selectedItems: MutableSet<String>`\n  - `toggleSelection(id)`, `clearSelection()`\n  - Preserves state across updates\n\n- **ConversationManager.kt**\n  - SharedPreferences \"conversations\" for list\n  - SharedPreferences \"msg_{convId}\" for messages\n  - Methods: getConversations(), saveConversation(), deleteConversation(), createNew(), getMessages(), saveMessages()\n\n- **Layouts**\n  - activity_main.xml: DrawerLayout wrapper\n  - drawer_content.xml: Custom drawer with action buttons\n  - item_conversation.xml: Checkbox + TextView\n  - item_message_user.xml: Copy + Edit buttons\n  - item_message_bot.xml: Copy + Edit buttons\n\n### Critical Patterns\n```kotlin\n// Preserve selection state\nval wasInSelectionMode = conversationAdapter?.isSelectionMode ?: false\nval previousSelections = conversationAdapter?.selectedItems?.toSet() ?: emptySet()\n// ... create new adapter ...\nif (wasInSelectionMode) {\n    conversationAdapter?.isSelectionMode = true\n    conversationAdapter?.selectedItems?.addAll(previousSelections)\n}\n\n// Safe loading message removal\nif (loadingPosition < chatMessages.size && chatMessages.getOrNull(loadingPosition)?.isLoading == true) {\n    chatMessages.removeAt(loadingPosition)\n    chatAdapter.notifyItemRemoved(loadingPosition)\n}\n\n// Cancel jobs before operations\nchatJob?.cancel()\nchatJob = null\n```\n\n### Storage Keys\n- \"conversations\" → \"list\" (JSON array)\n- \"conversations\" → \"msg_{convId}\" (JSON array)\n- \"app_prefs\" → \"last_conv_id\", \"api_key\", \"dark_mode\", \"model\"\n\n### API URLs\n- Chat: `https://gen.pollinations.ai/v1/chat/completions`\n- Image: `https://gen.pollinations.ai/v1/images/generations`\n- Proxy: `https://aivision-proxy.universeking.workers.dev`\n- Direct Image (no key): `https://image.pollinations.ai/prompt/{prompt}?width=1024&height=1024&model=flux&nologo=true`\n\n## TOOLS EXECUTED\n- Created 10+ drawable icons (ic_send, ic_delete, ic_add, ic_menu, etc.)\n- Modified activity_main.xml with DrawerLayout\n- Created drawer_content.xml with selection action buttons\n- Created item_conversation.xml with checkbox\n- Updated ConversationAdapter with multi-select logic\n- 38 commits pushed to main branch\n- Latest APK: v0.0.38 in `/storage/emulated/0/Download/AIChat-v0.0.38.apk`\n\n## NEXT STEPS\n1. **Add delete button to messages** (CURRENT REQUEST)\n   - Add delete icon to item_message_user.xml and item_message_bot.xml\n   - Wire up cli